<Layout title="About">

<section class="py-20 max-w-2xl space-y-6">

  <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">About</h1>

  <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
    ML Engineer with a background in applied machine learning across scientific and medical domains.
  </p>

  <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
    Current focus is on performance, numerical stability, and GPU-efficient model design, with ongoing work in CUDA and low-level optimisation.
  </p>

  <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
    Experience spans research, applied ML systems, and industry engineering roles.
  </p>

</section>

</Layout>
